            </p>

            <div className="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
               <div className="glass px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <div className="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-orange-500 animate-pulse"></div>
                  <span className="text-[9px] font-bold tracking-widest text-white/50 uppercase">Current Focus</span>
               </div>
               <div className="glass px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10">
                  <span className="text-[9px] font-bold tracking-widest text-white/30 uppercase">Future Roadmap</span>
